metadata.name: Noise #12
metadata.description:
Noise is a series of 175 unique 3d animations each paired with original music, created by Pat Dimitri.  Noise is the intersection of chaos and order. It explores the relationship between space and the lack thereof. It represents our best attempts to maneuver the world by understanding the relationship of the things we can control, with the things we cannot.

Noise exists to help block out the noise. Whether it be for 20 seconds or 20 years.
